      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/sqa-mrl3-criteria",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (OpenFOAM v9) is maintained under version-controlled software quality assurance procedures including unit tests, regression test suite, and documented release notes. All simulation scripts are under Git version control with tagged releases. SQA documentation reviewed and found to exceed MRL 3 requirements. Achieved level 3 against required level 2."
